{"abstract": "Tim Pool, who most recently worked for Vice Media, is known for his tech-driven eyewitness reporting during events in Ferguson, Mo., and at the Occupy Wall Street protests.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2014/09/08/business/media/fusion-expected-to-name-tim-pool-its-director-of-media-innovation.html", "snippet": "Tim Pool, who most recently worked for Vice Media, is known for his tech-driven eyewitness reporting during events in Ferguson, Mo., and at the Occupy Wall Street protests.", "lead_paragraph": "Fusion, the joint online and television venture between Univision and the Disney-ABC Television Group, is expected to announce on Monday that it has hired Tim Pool, a digital journalist known for his use of cutting-edge reporting technologies and his marathon live-stream reporting during the recent controversy in Ferguson, Mo., and the Occupy Wall Street protests.", "print_section": "B", "print_page": "7", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/09/08/business/fusion/fusion-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 427, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2014/09/08/business/fusion/fusion-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 427}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/09/08/business/fusion/fusion-jumbo.jpg", "height": 729, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/09/08/business/fusion/fusion-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 1457, "width": 2048, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/09/08/business/fusion/fusion-thumbStandard.jpg", "height": 75, "width":